{"tid":1752994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老味 九龍城食撚屎啦","createTime":"2019-11-25T00:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T03:15:49.000Z","uid":98915,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"41d06ad33d8e5c5db19d4229d7c72617929d3868","tid":1752994,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"嗱首先有投票嘅手足 唔好意思<br />\n錫返晒你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好愛你地嘅 啜返幾啖先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我屌你老味 一個區送咗10個議席出去<br />\n<br />\n先得25個議席 究竟入邊可以紅成點<br />\n<br />\n觀塘區40個議席依家都仲係點緊12個咋喎<br />\n<br />\n入邊嗰班廢老聽住 好話唔好聽<br />\n<br />\n香港依個時勢都仲咁撚樣<br />\n<br />\n你地都三份二隻腳入棺材啦 唔好再阻撚住後生發展<br />\n<br />\n之前我哋仲辛辛苦苦爭取埋啲咩全民退休保障<br />\n<br />\n攞去填海都唔益你班冚家剷啦<br />\n<br />\n等你哋死晒一定要光復九龍城"},{"pid":"4be3a6b2e9a8892d3918da00c5feebcd9e3ac4a5","tid":1752994,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:55:49.000Z","msg":"懷疑係因為舊樓多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be02fd340e1aadb4cb64964ef041bf60de720dd7","tid":1752994,"uid":140552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:56:49.000Z","msg":"九龍城真係好撚多廢老<br />\n啟德又係支那集中營"},{"pid":"93c6a2f9084125e88d82f8cdbf6b60dd6858bd3b","tid":1752994,"uid":60835,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:58:47.000Z","msg":"主要原因係，九龍城由6月到而家都未食過tg,黃大仙都多廢老，但一食完tg就覺醒曬"},{"pid":"8f5d45b363dc17d06eae4017f4a88aad01a5ed1d","tid":1752994,"uid":280612,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"仲要等佢地死哂先光復？拿拿聲請佢地食tg延年益壽啦"},{"pid":"78a42fd5929a67461b39cdf5497b52dd3e6c2bdb","tid":1752994,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84bb3946fd052714974ff6add7d2bf308668c3a","tid":17529